{"Sid":0,"Did":19120,"Id":"289370","Title":"心豆","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/object/2020-02-24/71143443-2a83-49e7-bfef-9c6172484062/collection/6948256a-59bb-46a0-aa8d-17ef02fc3e8b/108-lit-cw-833-201911111549015dc8cdcce7fbb0.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/object/2020-02-24/71143443-2a83-49e7-bfef-9c6172484062/collection/37401e93-973e-4bc3-a40e-da089f4c77e8/108-lit-cw-833-201911181821455dd2075868fd50.gif","IndexCode":"Culture_Object","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n本書分為五輯，輯一以真摯的情感描寫與親近家人的相處，〈阿嬤〉紀念祖母，〈那枚美麗的落日〉寫首次帶母親出國旅遊過程及內心的感慨。輯二〈鄉居〉、〈青蔬，親蔬〉、〈房間三疊〉等篇章，分別書寫田野自然、閒適的日常與甘美的兒時回憶。輯三文章多數選摘自作者與兩位好友──陳維鸚、蘇麗春所合著的一部作品，分享宜蘭在地旅遊。輯四敘身邊人事，〈薄荷功課〉、〈午餐時間〉生動帶出與學生互動的點滴。輯五，其關愛動物的心情表露無遺。作者透過回憶、觀察、探索，敘他人事，述自己情，為自身生命歷程留下深刻的記錄。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.7450148","Keyword_Latitude":"24.7484187","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/object/650606C1-671B-404D-AB7B-C54C8C2388CA","Original_Identifier":"289370","Keyword_Subject_1":"藝術與人文","alias":"","alternativeHeadline":"","Keywords":"《心豆》 / 陳維鸚 / 黃春美 / 蘇麗春","dates":"出版日期 / 2009/12/01","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/24 13:56:14","Creator":"黃春美","publisher":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","mediaType":"圖書及手冊","language":"","timelines":"戰後時期(1945~)","city":"宜蘭縣宜蘭市","address":"興路二段101號","lng":"121.7450148","lat":"24.7484187","contributors":"","contributor":"黃憲作;王怡云","size":"","admin":"","award":"","character":"","contentLocation":"","acquireWay":"","acquireSource":"","storage":"","version":"","isbn":"978-986-02-1410-9","onlineAuthLink":"","stuff":"","url":"","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","citation":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/object/2020-02-24/71143443-2a83-49e7-bfef-9c6172484062/collectionOpen/0bd299a3-4b1c-4ca5-a45b-b2d03b4ad6c8/108-lit-cw-833-re-201911181822025dd2075868fd50.jpg"}}